<codeline lineno="8"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>The<sp/>`OptimizerConfig`<sp/>class,<sp/>implemented<sp/>in<sp/>Cython,<sp/>serves<sp/>as<sp/>a<sp/>configuration<sp/>container<sp/>for<sp/>various<sp/>optimization<sp/>parameters<sp/>within<sp/>the<sp/>AnalysisG<sp/>framework.<sp/>It<sp/>provides<sp/>a<sp/>structured<sp/>and<sp/>efficient<sp/>way<sp/>to<sp/>define<sp/>and<sp/>manage<sp/>settings<sp/>for<sp/>different<sp/>optimizers,<sp/>leveraging<sp/>an<sp/>underlying<sp/>C++<sp/>`optimizer_params_t`<sp/>structure<sp/>for<sp/>high-performance<sp/>access<sp/>and<sp/>manipulation.<sp/>This<sp/>class<sp/>is<sp/>crucial<sp/>for<sp/>fine-tuning<sp/>the<sp/>training<sp/>process<sp/>of<sp/>machine<sp/>learning<sp/>models<sp/>by<sp/>allowing<sp/>precise<sp/>control<sp/>over<sp/>optimizer<sp/>behavior.</highlight></codeline>
